by ogizanagi at 2017-08-31T18:48:40Z

The conflict rule is not needed (at least for the tests to pass), dev-dependencies are installed for testing the FrameworkBundle, and the min version already is set to `^3.4`.
I think the issue comes from the fact packagist is only seeing 0898e9f01e1dedc70fb4f77b594227619d7e1711 [as last commit on `symfony/form:master`](https://packagist.org/packages/symfony/form#dev-master), hence the command is not available yet.
But 3.4 has properly been merged on master though: https://github.com/symfony/form/commits/master

